3. GRAND POPULARITY OF C
------------------------------------------------------------------

After the arrival of C , many to marked as beginning of modern age of computer languages. It has successfully
synthesised all attributes that lacks in the earlier languages.
The main strength of C was --

1. Powerful as well as easy to understand
2. Efficient in heavy tasks
3. Structured language , no more spaghetti code issues


Very soon, C becomes the most popular and used language across the world. It was said to be first Programmers' own
language. It was suitable for both academics , real time workers as well as research purposes. C was quickly adopted
so that many followers dedicated to the language similar to dedicated to divine gods .

